# Green AI — Crop Disease Detection
## Model Handoff Document · v1.0 · March 2026

**From:** AI/ML Team
**For:** Android & iOS Development Team
**Status:** Models trained, quantized, and ready for integration

---

## 1. What This System Does

A **two-stage on-device AI pipeline** that identifies crop diseases from a single leaf photograph. Fully offline — no internet required at inference time.

**User flow:**
1. Farmer opens app → selects crop type (Citrus / Rice / Sugarcane)
2. Takes a photo of the leaf
3. App runs Stage 1 → determines if diseased
4. If diseased, runs Stage 2 → identifies the specific disease
5. Result displayed with confidence score

---

