  "confidence": 91.3,
  "crop": "rice",
  "stage1_confidence": 94.0,
  "all_probabilities": {
    "Rice_brownleafspot": 0.913,
    "Rice_falsesmut": 0.051,
    "Rice_leafblight": 0.024,
    "Rice_planthopper": 0.012
  }
}
```
```json
{
  "result": "healthy",
  "disease": null,
  "confidence": 97.2,
  "crop": "citrus"
}
```

