## 9. Performance Benchmarks (Expected)

| Device | Stage 1 | Stage 2 | Total |
|---|---|---|---|
| Mid-range Android (Snapdragon 680) | ~80ms | ~350ms | ~430ms |
| High-end Android (Snapdragon 8 Gen 2) | ~20ms | ~90ms | ~110ms |
| iPhone 13 (A15 Bionic) | ~15ms | ~70ms | ~85ms |
| iPhone 11 (A13 Bionic) | ~25ms | ~110ms | ~135ms |

*Benchmarks are estimates based on INT8 quantized `.ptl` models running on CPU. Enable Neural Engine (iOS) or NNAPI (Android) for additional speedup.*

